Package: actuaRE
Type: Package
Title: Handling Hierarchically Structured Risk Factors using Random Effects Models
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Bavo D.C. Campo
Maintainer: Bavo D.C. Campo <bavo.decock@kuleuven.be>
Description: Using this package, you can fit a random effects model using either the hierarchical credibility model, a combination of the hierarchical credibility model with a GLM or a Tweedie generalized linear mixed model.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0), stats, methods, cplm
Imports: statmod, nlme, lme4, magrittr, speedglm, data.table, ggplot2, knitr
Suggests: 
    plyr,
